          },
          {
            "id": "mqvoenm2cf3p92",
            "label": " 宜宾学院",
            "expanded": true,
            "attachments": [
              {
                "id": "mqvxl42rjgckga",
                "type": "note",
                "name": "笔记_2026-06-27",
                "data": "<div class=\"title\" style=\"padding: 0px 0px 20px; list-style: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, arial, verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><h3 style=\"list-style: none; font-weight: 400; color: rgb(159, 8, 12); font-size: 20px; text-align: center;\">2026年招生章程</h3><div style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; text-align: center;\"><em style=\"list-style: none;\">发布者：</em> <em style=\"list-style: none;\">[发表时间]：2026年05月21日 14:28 </em><em style=\"list-style: none;\">[来源]： </em><em style=\"list-style: none;\">[浏览次数]：<span id=\"dynclicks_wbnews_2429_656\" name=\"dynclicks_wbnews_2429_656\" style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">2184</span></em></div></div><div id=\"vsb_content\" class=\"single-content\" style=\"list-style: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, arial, verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal;\"><div class=\"v_news_content\" style=\"list-style: none;\"><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">第一章</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">总</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">则</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第一条</span> <span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px; background: rgb(250, 252, 253);\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">为了深入贯彻实施招生工作</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">“阳光工程”，确保学校招生工作的顺利进行，切实维护广大考生和学校的合法权益，根据《中华人民共和国教育法》《中华人民共和国高等教育法》和其它法律法规的有关规定，结合我校招生工作实际，特制定本章程。</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第二条</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">宜宾学院是四川省省属公办全日制普通本科高等学校，位于万里长江第一城</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">——四川省宜宾市。学校现有江北老校区（A区、B区）和临港新校区，</span></span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">A校区（注册地）地址：四川省宜宾市翠屏区酒圣路8号</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">，</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">B校区地址：四川省宜宾市翠屏区敬业路146号</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">，</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">临港校区地址：四川省宜宾市翠屏区大学路三段</span>5号。</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">主管部门是四川省教育厅，本科专业基准学制为四年。</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第三条</span> <span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">在规定年限内，学生完成规定的课程和学分，符合毕业条件的，颁发经教育部电子注册的</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">“普通高等学校毕业证书”；达到授予学士学位条件的，颁发“学士学位证书”。颁发证书学校为宜宾学院。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">第二章</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">组织机构</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第四条</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">学校设立由校领导和有关职能部门主要负责人组成的招生工作委员会，负责贯彻执行国家招生政策，制定学校招生工作的有关规定，研究决定招生工作中的重大问题。</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第五条</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">招生就业处是学校组织和实施全日制本科招生工作的常设机构。</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第六条</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">学校招生工作监督组负责监督招生工作政策和规定的落实，受理招生工作中的有关举报，维护广大考生和学校的合法权益。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">第三章</span> <span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">招生计划</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第七条</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">学校根据四川省教育厅核定下达的招生计划，结合经济社会发展需要、学校发展规划、办学条件、毕业生就业情况和各省（自治区、直辖市）生源情况，制定各专业招生计划，经学校招生工作委员会审定，并报四川省教育厅批准后执行。</span></span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">第四章</span> <span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">录取规则</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第八条</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">严格执行国家招生政策和纪律，贯彻公平竞争、公正选拔、公开透明的原则，德智体美劳全面考核、综合评价、择优录取。</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第九条</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">男女比例要求：无男女生比例限制。</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第十条</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">普通类专业录取规则</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">1、认可国家和各省（自治区、直辖市）规定的各项加分政策，录取及分专业均以投档成绩为准。</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><a name=\"_Hlk195266091\" style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 14px;\"></a><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\"><a name=\"OLE_LINK4\" style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 14px;\"></a><a name=\"_Hlk195274093\" style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 14px;\"></a><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">2、非高考综合改革省（自治区、直辖市）的招生录取工作，执行“分数优先、遵循志愿”的原则，</span><a name=\"OLE_LINK3\" style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 14px;\"></a><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">不设专业志愿分数级差，</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">按投档成绩从高到低排序确定录取专业。投档成绩相同时，按生源省份确定的同分排序规则进行录取。生源省份没有统一排序规则规定的，依次按单科语文、数学、外语、文（理）综合的分数从高到低排序。</span><a name=\"OLE_LINK1\" style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 14px;\"></a><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">当考生所填专业志愿都无法满足时，若</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">考生服从专业调剂，则调剂到生源所在省招生计划未录满专业录取，</span><a name=\"OLE_LINK2\" style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 14px;\"></a><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">若考生不服从专业调剂，将作退档处理。</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">3、实行高考综合改革省（自治区、直辖市）的招生录取工作，按照各省（自治区、直辖市）公布的改革方案和有关办法执行。考生须满足我校选考科目要求，选考科目要求以省级招办向社会公布的为准。执行“分数优先、遵循志愿”的原则，不设专业志愿分数级差，按投档成绩从高到低排序确定录取专业。投档成绩相同时，按</span><a name=\"OLE_LINK5\" style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 14px;\"></a><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">生源省份</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">确定的同分排序规则进行录取。生源省份没有统一排序规则规定的，依次按语文数学两科之和、语文数学两科中单科最高成绩、外语单科成绩、首选科目单科成绩、再选科目单科最高成绩、再选科目单科次高成绩由高到低排序。</span></span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 20px;\">以院校专业组投档的，</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">当考生所填专业志愿都无法满足时，若</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 20px;\">服从专业调剂，只能在考生所投档的专业组内进行调剂。</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">若考生不服从专业调剂，将作退档处理。</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第十一条</span><strong style=\"list-style: none;\"> </strong><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">艺术体育类专业录取规则</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">专业成绩以各省（自治区、直辖市）统一组织的专业考试成绩为准，仅录取专业与文化成绩双上省控线考生。</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">1、在进档考生中，按投档成绩依据分数优先原则排序录取及安排专业，若投档成绩相同，则按专业成绩从高到低排序录取，专业成绩相同时再按文化成绩从高到低排序录取。</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">2、音乐表演专业：声乐只招收民族、美声考生，器乐只招收钢琴、竹笛、手风琴、古筝、小提琴、琵琶、箜篌、阮、柳琴、萨克斯、二胡考生。</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第十二条</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">语种要求：英语专业限招英语语种且加试口语合格的考生；日语专业限招外语口语合格的考生；其余专业外语语种不限，考生进校后均以英语为公共必修课安排教学（日语、俄语除外）。</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">第十三条</span> </span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">考生身体状况需符合教育部、卫生部、中国残联联合印发的《普通高等学校招生体检工作指导意见》和有关补充规定的要求</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">，身体疾病情况以高考体检表为准，对无法正常完成学业或体检表上提示学校可以不予录取的考生将不予录取，存在明显身体残疾或语言（或听力）障碍</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">的考生，请谨慎填报师范或表演类相关专业。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px 0px; list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: center; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; font-family: 黑体; font-size: 21px;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">第五章</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">收费标准及其他</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第十四条</span> <span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">学生的学费和住宿费标准严格按照省发展改革委、教育厅、财政厅、省市场监管局有关政策执行。服务性收费和代收费按照规定的项目，坚持学生自愿、不得营利的原则收取。</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第十五条</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">为保证家庭经济困难学生顺利完成学业，我校形成了完整的以奖、助、贷、勤、补、免、偿、捐为主的多元化资助帮扶体系。家庭经济特别困难的学生可通过申请生源地助学贷款、国家助学金、勤工助学等多种途径缓解经济压力并顺利完成学业。资助政策及程序详见宜宾学院学生工作处网站：</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">https://xsgzc.yibinu.edu.cn/。</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第十六条</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">新生入学后，学校将进行全面复查。经复查不合格者或弄虚作假者，将视不同情况予以处理，直至取消入学资格。</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第十七条</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">学校未授权、委托任何中介机构进行招生工作。</span></span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第十八条</span><strong style=\"list-style: none;\"> </strong><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">联系方式如下：</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">1、招生咨询电话：0831-3545029</span></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">2、学校网址：</span><a href=\"http://www.yibinu.edu.cn/\" style=\"list-style: none; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">https://www.yibinu.edu.cn</span></a></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">3、招生网址：</span><a href=\"http://www.yibinu.cn/\" title=\"宜宾学院\" style=\"list-style: none; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">https://zsw.yibinu.edu.cn</span></a></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">4、Email：</span><a href=\"mailto:ybxyzsb@126.com\" style=\"list-style: none; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">ybxyzsk@yibinu.edu.cn</span></a></p><p style=\"list-style: none; font-size: 12px; text-indent: 43px; line-height: 40px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 楷体; font-size: 21px;\">第十九条</span><span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%; text-align: center; font-family: 仿宋; font-size: 21px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"margin: 10px 0px 0px; list-style: none; width: 100%;\">本章程自公布之日起执行，由学校招生就业处负责解释。</span></span></p></div></div>",
                "mime": "text/html",
                "size": 26212,
                "comment": "",
                "createdAt": "2026-06-27T05:40:14.691Z"
              }
            ],
            "children": [],
            "fillColor": "#66bb6a",
            "textColor": "#0d47a1",
            "nodeWidth": null,
            "fontSize": null,
            "textAlign": null,
            "sideNotes": [],
